    "While conversing with humans in plain language, LLMs can reason and perform logical deduction.",
    "Recently, the ChatGPT Advanced Data Analysis (ADA), formerly known as ChatGPT Code Interpreter, has been made available as an extension and beta feature that may be used to analyze data and math problems, create charts, and write, execute, and refine computer code 16.",
